description: Try our easy to follow Baked Salmon Frittata recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Baked Salmon Frittata Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Reduce heat to low and cook for 10-12 minutes or until egg sets around edges. Put pan under preheated grill and cook for 5 minutes or until eggs are set and frittata is golden. Stand for 5 minutes. Serve with rocket.
